name: Change_Type
description: An indicator showing if the payment record is New, Added, Changed, or Unchanged in the current publication compared to the previous publication. NEW - To identify "new" records added from the end of the previous submission deadline until the current submission period deadline date ADDED - To identify records that were not eligible at the time of previous publication, which is eligible for current publication. CHANGED - To identify previously published records modified after the last publication. UNCHANGED - To identify previously published records that remain "unchanged" in current publication.  NEW  VARCHAR 2(20) string  20
